                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360919-2051-offence-1 t18360919-cd-33"></join>16th of September</rs>, putting him in fear, and taking from his person, and against his will, 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 cap, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 leaf of bread, value 3<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; 1 six-pence, 3 pence, and 6 half-pence, his goods and monies.</rs>
