               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Look round the court, and see if you see the man here who robbed you? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No—I do not know him very well—(<hi rend="italic">hesitating, and looking at the prisoner</hi>)—at that is the man.</p>
